{
  "body": "You are designing a softly lit pastel illustration featuring a character in a summer setting.\n\nCONTENT BRIEF\n- Character description: {{character}}\n- Scene setting: {{setting}}\n- On-image copy, if applicable: {{copy}}\n\nSTYLE DIRECTION\n- Genre / medium: pastel-toned anime-style illustration\n- Composition: vertical portrait orientation (3:2 aspect ratio), subject positioned slightly off-center within the frame with balanced negative space\n- Lens / camera: illustrative rendering with a focus on delicate linework and subtle depth\n- Lighting: soft diffuse daylight with a warm, slightly golden tone; gentle shadows with smooth transitions\n- Color palette and grading: pale pastel blues, whites, and golds; muted and harmonious tones to evoke a calm summer atmosphere\n- Texture / surface: delicate shading with smooth gradients and clean line art\n- Post-processing: subtle glow effects and minimal halation\n- Mood: serene, delicate, summery, breezy\n- References: Studio Ghibli-inspired color harmony, modern anime character design, soft pastel illustration techniques\n\nDESIGN RULES\n- Aspect: 3:2 portrait (~1024×1536) suitable for standalone artwork or character design\n- Ensure soft gradients and smooth transitions between colors\n- Maintain a clean and harmonious composition with ample negative space around the subject\n\nAVOID\n- Overly saturated or neon colors\n- Harsh or dramatic shadows\n- Busy backgrounds that distract from the character\n- Overcomplicated details that disrupt the delicate aesthetic\n\nAdditional constraints: {{extra}}\n\n——————\nCharacter: {{character}}\nScene setting: {{setting}}\nOn-image copy: {{copy}}\nAdditional constraints: {{extra}}",
